{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Col|2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","chapter":2,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":1,"text":"For I want you to know how greatly I am struggling for you, for those in Laodicea, and for all who have not seen me in person.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":2,"text":"I want their hearts to be encouraged and joined together in love, so that they may have all the riches of complete understanding and have the knowledge of God’s mystery —Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":3,"text":"In him are hidden all the treasures of wisdom and knowledge.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":4,"text":"I am saying this so that no one will deceive you with arguments that sound reasonable.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":5,"text":"For I may be absent in body, but I am with you in spirit, rejoicing to see how well ordered you are and the strength of your faith in Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":6,"text":"So then, just as you have received Christ Jesus as Lord, continue to walk in him,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":7,"text":"being rooted and built up in him and established in the faith, just as you were taught, and overflowing with gratitude.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":8,"text":"Be careful that no one takes you captive through philosophy and empty deceit based on human tradition, based on the elements of the world, rather than Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":9,"text":"For the entire fullness of God’s nature dwells bodily in Christ,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":10,"text":"and you have been filled by him, who is the head over every ruler and authority.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":11,"text":"You were also circumcised in him with a circumcision not done with hands, by putting off the body of flesh, in the circumcision of Christ,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":12,"text":"when you were buried with him in baptism, in which you were also raised with him through faith in the working of God, who raised him from the dead.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":13,"text":"And when you were dead in trespasses and in the uncircumcision of your flesh, he made you alive with him and forgave us all our trespasses.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":14,"text":"He erased the certificate of debt, with its obligations, that was against us and opposed to us, and has taken it away by nailing it to the cross.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":15,"text":"He disarmed the rulers and authorities and disgraced them publicly; he triumphed over them in him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":16,"text":"Therefore, don’t let anyone judge you in regard to food and drink or in the matter of a festival or a new moon or a Sabbath day.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":17,"text":"These are a shadow of what was to come; the substance is Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":18,"text":"Let no one condemn you by delighting in ascetic practices and the worship of angels, claiming access to a visionary realm. Such people are inflated by empty notions of their unspiritual mind.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":19,"text":"They don’t hold on to the head, from whom the whole body, nourished and held together by its ligaments and tendons, grows with growth from God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":20,"text":"If you died with Christ to the elements of this world, why do you live as if you still belonged to the world? Why do you submit to regulations:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":21,"text":"“Don’t handle, don’t taste, don’t touch”?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":22,"text":"All these regulations refer to what is destined to perish by being used up; they are human commands and doctrines.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","bookOrder":50,"chapter":2,"verse":23,"text":"Although these have a reputation for wisdom by promoting self-made religion, false humility, and severe treatment of the body, they are not of any value in curbing self-indulgence.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Col","chapter":2,"paragraphStarts":[1,4,6,8,16,20],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":4,"text":"Christ versus the Colossian Heresy"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I want you to know how greatly I am struggling "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 4:7","book":"2Ti","chapter":4,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" for you, for those in Laodicea, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:13–16","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:11","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:14","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and for all who have not seen me in person. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Tm 4:7","book":"2Ti","chapter":4,"verse":7},{"label":"Col 4:13–16","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":13},{"label":"Rv 1:11","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"Rv 3:14","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I want their hearts to be encouraged "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 16:25","book":"Luk","chapter":16,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:8","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and joined together in love, so that they may have all the riches of complete understanding and have the knowledge of God’s mystery "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:8","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" —Christ. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read mystery of God, both of the Father and of Christ; other ms variations exist on this v."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:27","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":27,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 16:25","book":"Luk","chapter":16,"verse":25},{"label":"Col 4:8","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":8},{"label":"Php 3:8","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":8},{"label":"Col 1:27","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read mystery of God, both of the Father and of Christ; other ms variations exist on this v."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In him are hidden all the treasures of wisdom "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 3:19","book":"Pro","chapter":3,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 11:2","book":"Isa","chapter":11,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 45:3","book":"Isa","chapter":45,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:5","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:22","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":22,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:21","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":21,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" and knowledge. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:6","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":6,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 3:19","book":"Pro","chapter":3,"verse":19},{"label":"Is 11:2","book":"Isa","chapter":11,"verse":2},{"label":"Is 45:3","book":"Isa","chapter":45,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 23:5","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":5},{"label":"Ac 7:22","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":22},{"label":"1Co 1:21","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":21},{"label":"1Co 14:6","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am saying this so that no one will deceive you with arguments that sound reasonable. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I may be absent in body, but I am with you in spirit, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 51:12","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:17","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" rejoicing to see how well ordered you are and the strength of your faith in Christ."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 51:12","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":12},{"label":"1Th 2:17","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So then, just as you have received "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Christ Jesus as Lord, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:11","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" continue to walk in him, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Eph 3:11","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"being rooted and built up in him "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:20","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and established in the faith, just as you were taught, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:21","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:9","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and overflowing with gratitude."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 2:20","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":20},{"label":"Eph 4:21","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":21},{"label":"Heb 13:9","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Be careful that no one takes you captive through philosophy and empty deceit based on human tradition, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 7:3","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" based on the elements of the world, rather than Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 6:20","book":"1Ti","chapter":6,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 7:3","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":3},{"label":"1Tm 6:20","book":"1Ti","chapter":6,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For the entire fullness "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:6","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:19","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of God’s nature dwells bodily "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or nature lives in a human body"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Christ, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 2:6","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"Col 1:19","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or nature lives in a human body"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and you have been filled by him, who is the head "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 11:3","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:22","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:15","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:23","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":23,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" over every ruler and authority. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 11:3","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":3},{"label":"Eph 1:22","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":22},{"label":"Eph 4:15","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":15},{"label":"Eph 5:23","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You were also circumcised in him with a circumcision not done with hands, by putting off the body of flesh, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:22","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:9","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the circumcision of Christ, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 1:17","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 1:22","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":22},{"label":"Col 3:9","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"Mt 1:17","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"when you were buried with him "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 6:4","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in baptism, in which you were also raised with him "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:1","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" through faith in the working of God, who raised him from the dead. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 17:9","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 20:9","book":"Jhn","chapter":20,"verse":9,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 21:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":14,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:24","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 6:4","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":4},{"label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"Col 3:1","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Mt 17:9","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":9},{"label":"Jn 5:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":25},{"label":"Jn 20:9","book":"Jhn","chapter":20,"verse":9},{"label":"Jn 21:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":14},{"label":"Ac 2:24","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And when you were dead in trespasses and in the uncircumcision of your flesh, he made you alive with him and forgave us all our trespasses. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He erased the certificate of debt, with its obligations, that was against us and opposed to us, and has taken it away by nailing it to the cross. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:23","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 23:26","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 9:23","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":23},{"label":"Lk 23:26","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He disarmed the rulers and authorities and disgraced them publicly; he triumphed over them in him. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or them through it"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:18","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:31","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":31,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 16:11","book":"Jhn","chapter":16,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:12","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:14","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"e"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 10:18","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":18},{"label":"Jn 12:31","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":31},{"label":"Jn 16:11","book":"Jhn","chapter":16,"verse":11},{"label":"Eph 6:12","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":12},{"label":"Heb 2:14","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or them through it"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, don’t let anyone judge "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:37","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" you in regard to food and drink "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:55","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":55,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:3","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:17","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 8:4","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:10","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":10,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" or in the matter of a festival or a new moon "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 81:3","book":"Psa","chapter":81,"verse":3,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" or a Sabbath day. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or or sabbaths"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 6:37","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":37},{"label":"Jn 6:55","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":55},{"label":"Rm 14:3","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":3},{"label":"Rm 14:17","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":17},{"label":"1Co 8:4","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":4},{"label":"Heb 9:10","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":10},{"label":"Ps 81:3","book":"Psa","chapter":81,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or or sabbaths"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These are a shadow "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:5","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:1","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of what was to come; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:38","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" the substance is "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or substance belongs to"},{"kind":"text","text":" Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:24","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":24,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:2","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 8:5","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":5},{"label":"Heb 10:1","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":1},{"label":"Rm 8:38","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":38},{"label":"Gl 3:24","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":24},{"label":"Gl 5:2","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or substance belongs to"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Let no one condemn "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or disqualify"},{"kind":"text","text":" you "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:24","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:14","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" by delighting in ascetic practices "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:12","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the worship of angels, claiming access to a visionary realm. Such people are inflated "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 4:6","book":"1Co","chapter":4,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" by empty notions of their unspiritual "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Lit fleshly"},{"kind":"text","text":" mind. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 9:24","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":24},{"label":"Php 3:14","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":14},{"label":"Col 3:12","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":12},{"label":"1Co 4:6","book":"1Co","chapter":4,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Or disqualify"},{"marker":4,"text":"Lit fleshly"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They don’t hold on to the head, from whom the whole body, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 6:13","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:4","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" nourished and held together by its ligaments and tendons, grows with growth from God."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 6:13","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":13},{"label":"Eph 4:4","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If you died with Christ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 6:8","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:24","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the elements of this world, why do you live as if you still belonged to the world? Why do you submit to regulations: "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 6:8","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":8},{"label":"1Pt 2:24","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Don’t handle, don’t taste, don’t touch”? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"All these regulations refer to what is destined to perish by being used up; they are human commands and doctrines. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Col:2:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Although these have a reputation for wisdom "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:22","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" by promoting self-made religion, false humility, and severe treatment of the body, they are not of any value in curbing self-indulgence. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit value against indulgence of the flesh"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 4:8","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 7:22","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":22},{"label":"1Tm 4:8","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit value against indulgence of the flesh"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099549656}